<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=413&amp;p=430#p430"><![CDATA[
7/25 (Sat.)Everything to know about ‘Triple Stimulus Vouchers’ plan/Where to Find the Best English Readers: 7 Incredible Sources for Endless English Reading Practice(Host Michelle)<br /><br />Session 1 : Everything to know about ‘Triple Stimulus Vouchers’ plan<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://chinapost.nownews.com/20200630-1460030">https://chinapost.nownews.com/20200630-1460030</a><!-- m --><br /><br />「振興三倍券」相關單字解析：<br />stimulus voucher 振興券<br />Triple Stimulus Vouchers 振興三倍券<br /><br />triple (adj.) 三倍的<br />stimulus (n.) 刺激品，激勵物<br />voucher (n.) 現金卷，代金券，票券<br /><br />▸People can go to the post offices to buy the stimulus vouchers.<br />▸The government hopes that the stimulus vouchers will boost domestic consumptions.<br /><br />stimulate (v.) 激發，激勵；促進<br />▸The tax cuts will stimulate consumption.<br />boost (v.) 改善；提高；增強；推動<br />▸The government managed to boost consumptions by the tax cuts.<br /><br />其他倍數怎麼說：<br />兩倍 double<br />三倍 triple<br />四倍 quadruple<br />五倍 quintuple<br /><br />( <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.takospace.com/main/ChannelAction?do=info&amp;p=8590#gsc.tab=0">https://www.takospace.com/main/ChannelA ... #gsc.tab=0</a><!-- m -->)<br /><br />另外，也可以使用times去表示：<br />5倍 five times/5 times<br />10倍 ten times/10 times<br />100倍 one hundred times/100 times<br /><br />Q1:Will you apply the Triple Stimulus Vouchers?<br />Q2:How do you plan to use this Triple Stimulus Vouchers? Is there any good way to use ?<br />Q3:How do you think that government release the triple stimulus vouchers with the aim of boosting the local economy before the end of December.Do you think it works?<br /><br />Session 2 :Where to Find the Best English Readers: 7 Incredible Sources for Endless English Reading Practice<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.fluentu.com/blog/english/english-readers/">https://www.fluentu.com/blog/english/english-readers/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25764">Michelle Hsu</a> — Fri Jul 24, 2020 11:32 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
